title: Models Jessica Harris and Selena Weber Pair Up for Bikini Shoot | TMZ.com
text:
Models Jessica Harris and Selena Weber Pair Up for Bikini Shoot Jessica Harris, Selena Weber Sandy Bottoms For the Win 1 2/24/2017 3:41 PM PST 
The mystery girl who had a 1 day fling in Miami with Scott Disick found herself a blonde friend ... and together they make a fantasstic team. 
Models Jessica Harris and Selena Weber got pretty sandy together for a shoot on Miami beach. J was nice enough to brush Selena's buns clean when it was all over. 
Kindness -- maybe that's what Scott saw in her . Yeah. That must be it.
